```json
{
  "application": "Gromacs",
  "details": {
    "software": [
      "Gromacs",
      "OpenMPI",
      "sed",
      "bc"
    ],
    "resource_requirements": {
      "nodes": 1,
      "time": "2 hours",
      "exclusive": true,
      "modules": [
        "mpi/openmpi"
      ]
    },
    "input_files": [
      "chamber_min.mdp",
      "spc216.gro",
      "topol.top",
      "posre.itp",
      "proline.gro",
      "proline.top",
      "${input}.pdb"
    ],
    "output_files": [
      "parameters.txt",
      "topol.top",
      "chamber_min.tpr",
      "chamber_min.trr",
      "chamber_min.xtc",
      "chamber_min.gro",
      "${output}.gro",
      "${Nmg}_${output}.gro",
      "${output}_box.gro",
      "${output}_solvated.gro"
    ],
    "description": "This script sets up, minimizes, and equilibrates a system to calculate the osmotic pressure of a given input structure, primarily amino acids."
  }
}
```
